-- Samantha Power to Replace Rice as UN Envoy, Official Says
-- B y   R o g e r   R u n n i n g e n
-- 2013-06-05T12:09:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-05/samantha-power-to-replace-rice-as-un-envoy-official-says.html
Samantha Power, who served as an
adviser on human rights to President Barack Obama in his first
term, will succeed  Susan Rice  as the U.S. ambassador to the
United Nations, a White House official said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
